reviews.review_text: Great Show! Beautiful Night of music, great recording.  Dan Healy really had the rear speakers doing crazy things at the Cap Center this and the next night.

Not epic, but decent I was there, but don't remember much apart from They Love Each Other being in the Sugaree spot. 
After a listen in the here and now- Nothing really stands out as epic, but no trainwrecks. A decent night with some good moments and worth a listen, just not a "best show ever".
